### Suppliers API Test Requests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7051
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Get All Suppliers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Supplier by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create New Supplier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "شركة الموردين المحدودة",
  "phone": "+966501234567",
  "email": "info@supplier.com",
  "address": "الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية",
  "websit": "https://supplier.com",
  "countryId": 1,
  "supplierNote": "مورد موثوق"
}

### Update Supplier
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "شركة الموردين المحدودة - محدث",
  "phone": "+966501234567",
  "email": "info@supplier.com",
  "address": "الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية",
  "websit": "https://supplier.com",
  "countryId": 1,
  "supplierNote": "مورد موثوق - محدث"
}

### Delete Supplier (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Suppliers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/search?name=شركة&email=supplier
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Supplier Offers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/suppliers/1/offers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get All Offers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Offer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/offers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

